      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand">ARK-1 Gideas</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-400">Autonomous crowd-magnet kiosk - launch 2026</p>
      <p class="mt-4"><strong>Status:</strong> In Development • Expected Q2 2026</p>
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none mt-6" >
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Key hardware & mobility</h3>
<ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
  <li>Full Steel <strong>ARK-chassis v1</strong> – breaks into 2-3 pieces for SUV transport.</li>
  <li>Twin hub-motors and two castor wheels</li>
  <li>Two fully automated Arms with full functioning fingers</li>
  <li>a big Touch-OLED display on chest for interaction</li>
  <li>Auto-docking charger – rolls home at 15 % battery.</li>
    <li>Fully automated mapped navigation.</li>

  
  <li>Tri-sensor nav: LiDAR, Intel RealSense Depth Camera, Face Detection Camera.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-2">Human+AI interaction</h3>
<ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
  <li>High quality LED face with many emotion morph targets.</li>
  <li>Dual 6-axis <strong>gesture arms</strong> (optional fixed-arm kit which is cheaper).</li>
  <li><strong>Persona-Engine</strong> – ChatGPT-based agent with pluggable “sarcastic”, “guide”, “fund-raiser” personalities.</li>
  <li>Depth-aware audience sizing &amp; heat-map; greets only approaching visitors.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-2">First customer</h3>
<p class="ml-6">
  <strong>UAE Red Crescent</strong> – configuring ARK-1 as a roaming donation agent
  (tap-to-give, animated thank-you sequence) – <em> In development</em> .
</p>

<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-2">Why no real pictures?</h3>
<p class="ml-6">
Simply because it isn't built yet. it is still in development but this is the vision of what the final version of the robot will be
</p>

